{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2121, "height": 2873, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "德仁后。", "block_bbox": [192, 259, 355, 309], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "2.襄阳郡：东汉建安十三年分南郡、南阳两郡各一部份置襄阳郡，当时辖地在今湖北省襄樊市、南漳县、宜城县、当阳县、远安县等一带，治所在襄阳（今湖北襄樊襄城区）。晋代杜预少子耽一支南渡襄阳，成为侨姓士族中的一员，其后裔杜依艺迁巩县，生杜审言，审言孙即大诗人杜甫。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 325, 1735, 573], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "3.中山郡：与京兆同源，三国魏仆射杜畿之后。自徐州刺史杜弼始有名人。", "block_bbox": [276, 590, 1694, 640], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "4.濮阳郡：古县名，原为春秋时期卫国都城，因地在濮水之北，故名。秦汉之际为濮阳县，属东郡，辖地在今河南省濮阳县。晋朝改东郡置国，西晋末期改郡，兵分济阴郡之一部分给濮阳郡。隋朝改为濮州。辖地在今河南省渭县、濮阳市、范县、山东省郭城县一带地区。杜赫之子杜威世居濮阳，其后至唐代有宰相杜鸿渐、杜暹。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 655, 1733, 975], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "成都、河东、齐郡、醴泉、河南。", "block_bbox": [281, 990, 930, 1041], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "5.洹水郡：与京兆同源，汉代杜延年之后。后赵从事中郎杜曼迁邺，复迁洹水，至唐，有宰相杜正伦。\n", "block_bbox": [186, 1057, 1732, 1174], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "6.陕郡：晋杜预后，有后魏广武太守杜德等。", "block_bbox": [279, 1192, 1133, 1243], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "7.安德郡：汉杜延年后，徙平原。", "block_bbox": [282, 1260, 922, 1310], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "8.扶风郡：居陕西郿县，唐有宗正少卿杜令怡。", "block_bbox": [282, 1327, 1176, 1379], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "9.偃师：出京兆，唐有礼部侍郎杜嗣光。", "block_bbox": [281, 1393, 1049, 1446], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "10.成都：魏初杜雄入蜀。", "block_bbox": [284, 1461, 768, 1511], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "11.河东：汉杜延年后，至唐有屯田员外郎杜颂等。", "block_bbox": [284, 1527, 1242, 1580], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "12.齐郡：汉杜延年后，唐有尚书令、吴王杜伏威。", "block_bbox": [285, 1593, 1241, 1647], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "13.醴泉：唐有检校右仆射、节度使杜希全。", "block_bbox": [284, 1662, 1112, 1714], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "14.河南：北魏鲜卑族独孤氏改姓杜氏。", "block_bbox": [284, 1730, 1028, 1781], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "除以上《元和姓纂》所载14个郡望外，还有2个郡望：", "block_bbox": [281, 1798, 1340, 1851], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "南阳郡：治所在今河南省南阳。以秦大将军杜赫居南阳，称杜衍，后裔世居此地。\n", "block_bbox": [190, 1866, 1734, 1990], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "汉阳郡：治所在今湖北省汉阳。", "block_bbox": [281, 2006, 887, 2058], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "二、堂号", "block_bbox": [285, 2076, 487, 2129], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜姓的堂号除了与郡望同名外，主要还有诗圣、少陵等堂号。", "block_bbox": [281, 2145, 1448, 2200], "block_id": 19, "block_order": 20}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "1.诗圣堂：历史上称唐朝大诗人杜甫为“诗圣”。", "block_bbox": [284, 2217, 1200, 2270], "block_id": 20, "block_order": 21}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "2.少陵堂：诗圣杜甫自号“少陵野老”。", "block_bbox": [280, 2288, 1031, 2338], "block_id": 21, "block_order": 22}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "3.宝田堂：出自宋杜孟的故事。杜孟，普州人，读书太学，官至尚书。为官清廉，且家教甚严，常训子孙曰：“忠孝吾家之宝，经史吾家之田。”时号宝田杜氏，后人遂以“宝田”为堂号。\n", "block_bbox": [187, 2356, 1738, 2545], "block_id": 22, "block_order": 23}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "6.武库堂：出自西晋杜预的故事。杜预，京兆杜陵（今陕西西安东南）人，", "block_bbox": [279, 2562, 1733, 2616], "block_id": 23, "block_order": 24}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1854, 753, 1935, 1481], "block_id": 24, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "三四〇", "block_bbox": [1869, 2161, 1924, 2289], "block_id": 25, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8631026744842529, "coordinate": [184.14019775390625, 655.3206176757812, 1733.687255859375, 975.0668334960938]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8396447896957397, "coordinate": [184.08819580078125, 325.4139404296875, 1735.152587890625, 573.8802490234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8231844305992126, "coordinate": [187.81732177734375, 2356.0908203125, 1738.98583984375, 2545.9326171875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8169687986373901, "coordinate": [190.97650146484375, 1866.674072265625, 1734.102294921875, 1990.69140625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7950389385223389, "coordinate": [285.30474853515625, 2076.2841796875, 487.3050537109375, 2129.7294921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7591753005981445, "coordinate": [186.670654296875, 1057.447021484375, 1732.4921875, 1174.900634765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7080200910568237, "coordinate": [279.69415283203125, 2562.533447265625, 1733.85595703125, 2616.486572265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6980111002922058, "coordinate": [192.6907958984375, 259.65533447265625, 355.42449951171875, 309.167236328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.692145049571991, "coordinate": [281.579833984375, 2006.429443359375, 887.4825439453125, 2058.022216796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6523556709289551, "coordinate": [276.288818359375, 590.3460083007812, 1694.85205078125, 640.5858764648438]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "t